      <h2>💡 Shocking Info Topics</h2>
      <span class="badge badge-blue" style="background:rgba(79,159,255,0.1);color:var(--blue);">5 High-Retention</span>
    </div>
    <div class="topics-grid" id="infoGrid"></div>

    <div class="footer-note">
      <span>⚡</span>
      <span>Ye topics <strong>real channel data</strong> ke analysis par based hain — tone, length, style sab study kiya gaya hai. Quality hook + sahi editing ke saath ye topics viral hone ke high chances hain. Topics channel ke actual pattern se match karte hain.</span>
    </div>

  </div>

